>> title: Ginger Mint Julep
>> tags: julep,mint,bourbon,ginger

Crush enough @ice for a #medium glass or julep cup{}. Add to cup.

In a #shaker{}, add @mint leaves{12} and muddle. If no muddler is handy, you can add a few cubes of ice and shake rapidly.

Fill shaker with ice. Add @Domaine de Canton ginger liqueuer{1/3%oz} and @bourbon or rye{2 1/2%oz}. Shake until well chilled.

Strain into cup with ice. Garnish with additional mint leaf.